{
  "stem": "15694.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it was so quiet that I said, this is the time to escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And like a few times before, the big question which must have happened thousands and thousands of times over, which thwarted the idea of escape, was the question of where to.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The countries of Europe were occupied, and maybe the engine will go to the front.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I wanted to think of something to make a rope, to step outside, because where were the guards, I thought.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Step outside in case somebody would come, I would climb back quickly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we had no ropes to put a coup-- put a couple of sheets together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But once an escape has been started, there's no coming back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, had we known what-- but nobody else did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So where are the so-called toughies and go-getters amongst the youngsters?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why did they-- well, maybe some did, but we didn't hear anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we waited as well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now my nerves were really bad at that time, and I fell into a kind of stupor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe half sleep or whatev-- whatever you'd like to call it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was woken up by a jerk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The engine was back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, coupled to the train, but at the rear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the train started moving and soon veered to the right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And once more it stopped, and when it stopped, what I didn't see before, every second train had a guard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The nearest to us was on the next wagon the other side, so not very near.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I were sitting on some ledges on top of the, you know, of the wagons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the train gathered speed.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
